cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a novel approach to reduce the communication complexity of Federated Learning, which is a subfield of Machine Learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with distributed computing and optimization, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper's focus on optimization and convergence rates also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
